30 Lokiyaduka, Kusalattika
Lokiyaduka, Kusalattika
39.
112Lokiyaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nalokuttaro nakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… . Hetuyā dve…pe…  avigate dve.
113Lokiyaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nalokuttaro naakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Hetuyā ekaṃ…pe…  avigate ekaṃ.
114Lokiyaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paccayā nalokiyo naabyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… . Hetuyā dve…pe…  avigate dve.
